1 An application that collects messages and files sent from different platforms. It will connect all messengers of the user and allow you to use them from one place.
Built-in filter will allow you to find necessary messages and chats. Sent files will receive a sender tag,
which will allow you to find them and identify the source.it is possible to implement the function of sending messages to yourself at a given time,
which will allow you to create a database of notes and reminders
2 An application that allows you to find by frame or audio fragment the film or TV series from which it was taken
3 The application collects medical data and gives the user a list of restrictions and recommendations; it can also remind you when to take medications
There are prospects for partnerships with companies in the medical field, and in this case it is possible to expand the base of functions
